Crocagile
========

Crocagile is an agile-inspired workspace that keeps your team together throughout the entire product life-cycle. Learn more at https://www.crocagile.com

Crocagile GitHub integration supports Task & User Story closing/reopening, with file modification tracking per-commit.

How To Install
-------------

1. Obtain your Project Key by visiting the settings area of your Crocagile project, at https://www.crocagile.com
2. Use your Project Key when setting up Crocagile GitHub services for your GitHub repository.
3. If your GitHub email address is not the same as your Crocagile address, append your commit messages with -email=[your crocagile email]
4. Visit https://blog.crocagile.com for a full list of supported integration commands.
